Interface BatchJobMutateResultInterface<O,E>

    public interface BatchJobMutateResultInterface<O,E>
extends Serializable
    The result of a single attempted operation from a batch job.

    • Method Detail

      • getOperand

        O getOperand()
        Returns the successfully modified object for the result. For a given result, either this will not be null or getErrorList() will not be null, but not both.

      • getErrorList

        BatchJobMutateResultInterface.BatchJobErrorListInterface<E> getErrorList()
        Returns the list of errors for the result. For a given result, either this will not be null or getOperand() will not be null, but not both.

      • getIndex

        Long getIndex()
        Returns the zero-based index of this result. This will be the same as the zero-based index of the corresponding operation that was uploaded to the batch job.
